headline: Agoda Highlights the Spirit of Hokkaido Ahead of Video Game Release
summary: Japan's Mount Yotei in Hokkaido prefecture is about to catch the eye of the global gaming community with a major video game focusing on the region scheduled to be released on October 2nd. Digital travel platform Agoda highlights the stunning natural landscapes of Hokkaido and encourages travelers to explore the breathtaking real-life inspirations behind the game's decor.
